# voicecli.vocab — personal vocabulary for speech recognition
# Copy this file to voicecli.vocab (gitignored) and add your own words.
#
# One word or phrase per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# These are injected into Whisper's initial_prompt to bias spelling.
# Works in French and English — just list the words as you want them spelled.
#
# Discovery: voicecli searches for voicecli.vocab by walking up from CWD to $HOME,
# same as voicecli.toml. A file at ~/projects/voicecli.vocab applies to all projects.

# ── People & products ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Claude
# Lyra
# VoiceCLI
# Roxabi

# ── Technical terms ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PyTorch
# Whisper
# Chatterbox

# ── French proper nouns ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (same list works for both languages — Whisper picks up spelling regardless)
